Package tech.hiddenproject.progressive.annotation

Contains useful annotations for auto dependency injection, game beans and more.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Autofill
    Represents field or constructor which can be injected with some value from Dependency Injection container.
    Components
    Point on specific classes DI container must look at.
    ComponentScan
    Asks Dependency Injection container to scan packages for beans.
    Configuration
    Used to mark class as bean provider for DIContainer.
    FromParent
    Marks field in GameScript to be filled from some parent GameObject's GameScript.
    GameBean
    Marks class or method as bean provider for Dependency Injection container.
    Intercept
    Used in BasicProxyCreator while proxy class creation from original class annotated with Proxy.
    IsGameScript
    Marks class as GameScript for GameObject.
    Proxy
    Used in BasicProxyCreator to create proxy class from original class annotated with Proxy.
    Qualifier
    Specifies bean name to inject into class field or method parameter.
    RequiredGameScript
    Defines required GameScripts for this GameScript.
